                                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                                    "actorId2": null,
                                                                    "text": "Hmm, there's a section on \"Tells\". If I watch the other players closely, I may see that they always look happy when they have a great hand. Except sneaky players may pretend to look sad instead. Or maybe they take a cookie and tear it in half when they think they're winning.",
