                                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                                    "actorId2": null,
                                                                    "text": "Hmmm. Poobah games are as much about playing people as about playing cards. I have to know when I'm beat so I don't waste more money on bad bets.",
