                                    "type": "nodes.playSoundEffect",
                                    "soundEffectName": "book_page_turn.wav",
                                    "wait": false
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "8e3adfa7-e60b-4a64-b513-bbae1d0ad001",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Middle hands are called \"Mimi\". They might be worth keeping at the beginning because I could draw into a Fizbin or even a Poobah. But a Mimi is just okay if I can't improve it.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d59b6f9a-c71d-4daa-b047-b47e17c288bf",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "A Meh hand is pretty bad. I should probably dump those rather than lose more money by calling bets with it. Might be worth bluffing once in a while. At least it beats a Wump. Wumps are the worst!",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
